      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. This car has been so well-loved and taken care of\u2014it's in great shape and drives like a dream! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, it\u2019s super reliable and ready to hit the road. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, so you can just hop in and enjoy the ride. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
