    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain delivers power through an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction out of apexes. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS system servicing and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement check. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. A mechanically robust example ready for the backroads.",
