    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior presents beautifully in its original finish, though a discerning eye will notice minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with well-preserved upholstery; the seats remain firm and supportive, showing only slight creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent comprehensive inspection, oil change, and tire rotation completed just last month. The engine runs quiet and smooth, while the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road today without any immediate maintenance needs.",
