    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered chassis. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent VANOS system refresh and valve adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, addressing the platform's primary structural weak point. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers. This is a driver-spec machine where mechanical integrity and throttle response have been prioritized over cosmetic perfection.",
